flowchart TD
    A[Multiple Excel files in folder] --> B[Tool reads all .xlsx files]
    B --> C{Check each file's headers}
    C -->|Valid headers| D[Add to merge list]
    C -->|Invalid headers| E[Skip file<br/>Report reason]
    
    D --> F[Combine all valid files]
    F --> G[Add source_file column<br/>showing original filename]
    G --> H[Format master file]
    H --> I[Bold headers<br/>Auto-size columns<br/>Freeze top row]
    I --> J[Save master Excel file]
    
    E --> K[Print report]
    J --> K
    K --> L[Shows merged files<br/>skipped files<br/>total rows]
    
    style A fill:#4A90D9,color:#fff
    style D fill:#3AAE6E,color:#fff
    style E fill:#E8913A,color:#fff
    style J fill:#3AAE6E,color:#fff
    style L fill:#7B68EE,color:#fff
